  VARIABLE
  BUNDLE
  COMBO
  SERVICE
  DIGITAL
  SERIALIZED
  BATCH_MANAGED
  PERISHABLE
  RAW_MATERIAL
  SEMI_FINISHED
  FINISHED_GOODS
  SUBSCRIPTION
